title: Sentimental kiss
description: Natsukawa Yuna lives with her busy junior high school teacher mother and her rebellious junior high school younger sister, Nana. She has her hands full with her family, house chores, and her part-time job, but one day she meets a beautiful younger boy in the midst of trouble. The destined love to unfold everything is now in motion!
author: KOMORI Mikko
